snippet.title: F1® Manager 24 | Feature Focus - Managing Mentality
snippet.description:
Learn more about the new Mentality System coming to F1® Manager 24 with the second episode of our Feature Focus deep dives series! Learn more: https://www.f1manager.com/features/new/managing-mentality

F1® Manager 24 releases on PC and consoles, July 23rd 2024. Pre-order Now: https://fron.dev/YT-F1M24-PO #f1manager23
